Package cs.ualberta.ca.tunein

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildConfig  
    Cache
    Model Cache Class: This is using a singleton design pattern.
    CacheActivity
    View CacheActivity Class: This part of the view of displaying saved comments that are saved to the cache.
    CacheController
    Controller CacheController Class: This controller is used to modify the cache list of a user.
    Comment
    Model Comment Class: This is class is part of the comment model.
    CommentCache
    Model CommentCache Class: This class is for modeling the comment cache, which will be a array list of comments that the user chooses to save.
    CommentController
    Controller CommentController class: This is a controller class that manipulates the comment model.
    Commenter
    Model Commenter Class: This is a model class for the user that creates a comment.
    CommentPageActivity
    View CommentPageActivity Class: Part of the view class that contains a comment and its replies.
    CommentViewAdapter
    View CommentViewAdapter Class: This class is used to create the list view for the topic list that contains comments.
    EditPageActivity
    View CommentPageActivity Class: Part of the view class that contains a comment that is editable.
    FavoriteActivity
    View FavoriteActivity Class: This class is part of the view of displaying favorites by using the comment view row.
    FavoriteController
    Controller FavoriteController Class: This class is used to modify the favorites list of a user.
    Favorites
    Model Favorites Class: This is using a singleton design pattern.
    GeoLocation
    Model GeoLocation Class: This class is a model of the geolocation of a comment, that holds the longitude and latitude of the comment.
    GeoLocationController
    Controller GeoLocationController Class: This class is to get the geoLocation of the application so it can be used in comment creation and for sorting comments based on location.
    Image
    Model Image Class: This is a model for the image of a comment and uses a bitmap to store the image of a comment.
    ImageController
    Controller ImageController Class: This is a controller used to upload images when creating or editing comments.
    MainActivity
    View MainActivity Class: This is part of the view for the main title page of the app.
    MainActivityProduct
    Controller MainActivityProduct class: This class is a utility class for the MainActivity class that gets/sets view elements and also helps the MainActivity class setup the app sorting.
    ProfileViewActivity
    View ProfileView Activity Class: This is part of the view class that will show the user the profile page that allows the user to view another user's profile and also allow the owner of the profile to edit their profile.
    R  
    R.attr  
    R.dimen  
    R.drawable  
    R.id  
    R.layout  
    R.menu  
    R.string  
    R.style  
    ReplyViewAdapter
    View ReplyViewAdapter Class: This is part of the view class for comments.
    ReplyViewAdapter.ViewHolder
    View holder that holds the elements of a custom row that improves scrolling.
    ThreadController
    Controller ThreadController Class: This is part of the controller that controls a list of comments and modifies the comments in the list passed to the controller.
    ThreadList
    Model Thread Class: This class is part of the comment model and holds a list of comments.
    TopicListActivity
    View TopicListActivity Class: This is part of the view of displaying the topic list of comments.
    UserController
    Controller UserController Class: This is a controller class that modifies the user model and will also be used to load a saved username.
